{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852015384,"sessionID":"ses_286fa7576ffeYv4Qt7A9uX3m2B","part":{"id":"prt_d7905bd86001XQ6vxXWN0MgyFD","messageID":"msg_d79058b70001cJhap20MB55Va8","sessionID":"ses_286fa7576ffeYv4Qt7A9uX3m2B","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"toolu_tool-8e8be6b4acec49cd8c3aa4f84c3a97af","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore OpenSpec change structure","prompt":"Explore this codebase to understand:\n1. Is there an existing changes/ directory structure?\n2. Are there any existing AR (Architectural Record) changes I can use as templates?\n3. Is there an OpenSpec manifest or configuration that defines the change scaffold format?\n4. Look for any AR-* directories or files that show the expected structure\n\nFocus on finding:\n- changes/ directory and its structure\n- Any AR-NNN example directories\n- Any manifest.yaml, SPEC.md, or similar OpenSpec files\n- Any README or documentation about the change process\n\nReturn a summary of:\n- The exact scaffold structure needed (directory names, required files)\n- Any template content patterns you find\n- The path where changes/AR-011/ should be created","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_286fa4256ffe2IvANmJXoNiz3Q (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nNow I have a complete understanding of the AR change structure. Here's my comprehensive summary:\n\n---\n\n## Summary: AR (Architectural Record) Change Scaffold Structure\n\n### 1. Existing changes/ Directory Structure\n\n**Yes, the `changes/` directory exists** at:\n```\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/\n```\n\nIt contains **10 existing AR directories** (AR-001 through AR-010).\n\n### 2. AR-* Example Directories Available\n\nThe following AR directories exist as templates:\n- `changes/AR-001/` - CRD AgentRuntime type definitions\n- `changes/AR-002/` - (with delta-spec.md)\n- `changes/AR-003/` - (no delta-spec.md)\n- `changes/AR-004/` - (no delta-spec.md)\n- `changes/AR-005/` - (with delta-spec.md)\n- `changes/AR-006/` through `changes/AR-010/` - all include delta-spec.md\n\n### 3. OpenSpec Manifest/Configuration\n\n**No `manifest.yaml` or `SPEC.md` found.** However, the following configuration files exist:\n- `.sdd_prompt.md` - Contains the prompt template for generating design.md\n- `project.md` - Project context and conventions\n- `proposal.md` - Root-level proposal (seems to be for AR-007)\n\n### 4. Exact Scaffold Structure Required\n\n**Standard 5-file structure** (based on most recent ARs):\n\n| File | Required | Purpose |\n|------|----------|---------|\n| `spec.md` | Yes | Basic metadata + scope definition |\n| `proposal.md` | Yes | Purpose, scope, impact analysis, alternatives, risks |\n| `design.md` | Yes | Technical implementation details, architecture, data structures |\n| `tasks.md` | Yes | Task checklist by phases, verification commands, acceptance criteria |\n| `delta-spec.md` | Yes (newer ARs) | GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios, implementation files |\n\n**Directory Structure:**\n```\nchanges/AR-011/\n├── spec.md\n├── proposal.md\n├── design.md\n├── tasks.md\n└── delta-spec.md\n```\n\n### 5. Template Content Patterns\n\n**spec.md template pattern:**\n```markdown\n# AR-NNN — [Title]\n\n## Metadata\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-NNN — [Title] |\n| Module | `pkg/xxx` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S/M/L |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n[Description]\n\n## Out of Scope\n- [Items]\n\n## Dependencies\n- [Items]\n\n## Deliverables\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| [Files] | [Descriptions] |\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] [Criteria]\n\n## References\n- [References]\n```\n\n**proposal.md template pattern:**\n```markdown\n# AR-NNN — [Title] Proposal\n\n## Purpose\n[Core purpose description]\n\n## Scope\n### In Scope\n| Deliverable | Description |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| [Items] | [Descriptions] |\n\n### Out of Scope\n- [Items]\n\n## Impact Analysis\n### Upstream Dependencies\n| Dependency | Impact |\n|------------|--------|\n| [Items] | [Impacts] |\n\n### Downstream Consumers\n| Consumer | Usage |\n|----------|-------|\n| [Items] | [Usages] |\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n### Alternative N: [Name]\n[Description with Pros/Cons table]\n\n## Risks\n| Risk | Mitigation |\n|------|------------|\n| [Items] | [Mitigations] |\n\n## Implementation Notes\n[ numbered notes]\n\n## References\n- [References]\n```\n\n**design.md template pattern:**\n```markdown\n# AR-NNN — [Title] Design\n\n## Overview\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-NNN — [Title] |\n| Module | `pkg/xxx` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S/M/L |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n## Architecture\n[ASCII diagrams]\n\n## Design\n### Component Relationships\n| Component | Role | Dependencies |\n|-----------|------|--------------|\n| [Items] | [Roles] | [Dependencies] |\n\n## Data Structures\n[Go code blocks]\n\n## API Contracts\n[Route tables, request/response formats]\n\n## Error Handling\n[Error types and handling strategy]\n\n## Testing Strategy\n[Test coverage goals and patterns]\n\n## Validation Checklist\n- [ ] [Items]\n\n## Open Questions\n[ numbered questions]\n\n## References\n- [References]\n```\n\n**tasks.md template pattern:**\n```markdown\n# AR-NNN — [Title] Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-NNN — [Title] |\n| Module | `pkg/xxx` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S/M/L |\n| Design | [Stage status] |\n\n## Task Checklist\n### Phase 1: [Name] (ST-1)\n- [ ] **T1.1**: [Task description]\n  - [Details]\n  - File: `pkg/xxx/file.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/xxx -run TestX -v`\n\n## Task Dependencies\n[ASCII dependency diagram]\n\n## Verification Commands\n| Task | Verification Command |\n|------|----------------------|\n| [Task] | [Command] |\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] [Criteria]\n\n## Files Modified/Created\n| File | Status | Description |\n|------|--------|-------------|\n| [Files] | Created/Modified | [Descriptions] |\n\n## Notes\n[Implementation notes]\n\n## Implementation Timeline\n| Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n|-------|-------|--------|------------|\n| [Phase] | [Tasks] | [Status] | [Percent] |\n```\n\n**delta-spec.md template pattern:**\n```markdown\n# Delta Spec: AR-NNN — [Title]\n\n**Module:** `pkg/xxx`\n**Language:** Go\n**Size:** S/M/L\n\n## Overview\n[Description placeholder or actual content]\n\n## GIVEN/WHEN/THEN Scenarios\n### Requirement: [Name]\n#### Scenario: [Name]\n- **GIVEN** [Condition]\n- **WHEN** [Action]\n- **THEN** [Result]\n\n## Implementation Files\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| [Files] | [Purposes] |\n\n## Dependencies\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| [Packages] | [Purposes] |\n\n## Validation Checklist\n- [ ] [Items]\n```\n\n### 6. Path Where AR-011 Should Be Created\n\n```\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/\n```\n\n**Required files:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/proposal.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/design.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/tasks.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/delta-spec.md`\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_286fa4256ffe2IvANmJXoNiz3Q","model":{"modelID":"glm-5","providerID":"bailian-coding-plan"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore OpenSpec change structure","time":{"start":1775851912614,"end":1775852015381}}}}
