{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852134575,"sessionID":"ses_286fa7576ffeYv4Qt7A9uX3m2B","part":{"id":"prt_d7907c0790010KKzPBEtNQSY92","messageID":"msg_d79077d99001gzS5l7ZDdjIyGh","sessionID":"ses_286fa7576ffeYv4Qt7A9uX3m2B","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-5eaa98d047c647adbb2de603d6e8b6dc","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/spec.md","content":"# AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发\n\n## Metadata\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 |\n| Module | `pkg/router` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n实现 Router 模块的 JWT 认证与签发功能，包括：\n- JWT Token 生成与签发\n- JWT Token 验证中间件\n- Token 刷新机制\n\n## Out of Scope\n- OAuth2 集成\n- 第三方身份提供商对接\n- 用户权限管理（RBAC）\n\n## Dependencies\n- 待分析\n\n## Deliverables\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `pkg/router/jwt.go` | JWT 核心功能实现 |\n| `pkg/router/jwt_test.go` | JWT 单元测试 |\n| `pkg/router/middleware/auth.go` | 认证中间件 |\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] JWT Token 签发功能正常\n- [ ] Token 验证中间件正确拦截无效请求\n- [ ] Token 刷新机制工作正常\n- [ ] 测试覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n\n## References\n- 待补充"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/spec.md","time":{"start":1775852134551,"end":1775852134574}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852134577,"sessionID":"ses_286fa7576ffeYv4Qt7A9uX3m2B","part":{"id":"prt_d7907f38a001i9icAiBDxdw6MC","messageID":"msg_d79077d99001gzS5l7ZDdjIyGh","sessionID":"ses_286fa7576ffeYv4Qt7A9uX3m2B","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-3ca035d0029e4f8f9baac2fb6ba9973d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/proposal.md","content":"# AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 Proposal\n\n## Purpose\n为 Router 模块提供标准化的 JWT 认证与签发能力，支持服务间安全通信和用户身份验证。\n\n## Scope\n### In Scope\n| Deliverable | Description |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| JWT 签发 | 生成标准 JWT Token |\n| Token 验证 | 中间件验证 Token 有效性 |\n| Token 刷新 | 支持长效 Token 的刷新机制 |\n\n### Out of Scope\n- OAuth2 协议实现\n- 第三方身份提供商集成\n- 细粒度权限控制\n\n## Impact Analysis\n### Upstream Dependencies\n| Dependency | Impact |\n|------------|--------|\n| pkg/config | 配置读取（密钥、过期时间） |\n| pkg/logger | 日志记录 |\n\n### Downstream Consumers\n| Consumer | Usage |\n|----------|-------|\n| HTTP Handlers | 认证中间件保护 |\n| gRPC Services | Token 验证 |\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n### Alternative 1: 使用现成 JWT 库\n| Pros | Cons |\n|------|------|\n| 成熟稳定 | 可能存在冗余功能 |\n| 社区支持 | 需要适配现有架构 |\n\n### Alternative 2: 自实现 JWT 逻辑\n| Pros | Cons |\n|------|------|\n| 完全可控 | 安全风险高 |\n| 轻量 | 维护成本高 |\n\n**推荐方案**: Alternative 1 - 使用成熟 JWT 库（如 golang-jwt/jwt）\n\n## Risks\n| Risk | Mitigation |\n|------|------------|\n| 密钥泄露 | 使用环境变量或密钥管理服务 |\n| Token 被劫持 | 支持 Token 黑名单机制 |\n| 时钟不同步 | 引入合理的时钟偏差容忍 |\n\n## Implementation Notes\n1. 使用 golang-jwt/jwt v5 作为基础库\n2. 支持 HS256 和 RS256 两种签名算法\n3. Token 默认过期时间 24 小时\n4. 刷新 Token 有效期 7 天\n\n## References\n- [golang-jwt/jwt](https://github.com/golang-jwt/jwt)\n- [RFC 7519 - JSON Web Token](https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7519)"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/proposal.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775852134555,"end":1775852134576}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852134578,"sessionID":"ses_286fa7576ffeYv4Qt7A9uX3m2B","part":{"id":"prt_d79085eb1001qkFBArEPyqFsPG","messageID":"msg_d79077d99001gzS5l7ZDdjIyGh","sessionID":"ses_286fa7576ffeYv4Qt7A9uX3m2B","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-0442eb2c33d74e1bbdf2a3bc335829b4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/design.md","content":"# AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 Design\n\n## Overview\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 |\n| Module | `pkg/router` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n## Architecture\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                      HTTP Request                            │\n└─────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────┘\n                      │\n                      ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                  JWT Middleware                              │\n│  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐         │\n│  │   Parser    │──│  Validator  │──│  Extractor  │          │\n│  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘         │\n└─────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────┘\n                      │\n                      ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    Handler                                   │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    JWT Service                               │\n│  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐         │\n│  │   Signer    │  │  Verifier   │  │  Refresher  │          │\n│  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘         │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐           │\n│  │           Key Manager (HS256/RS256)          │           │\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘           │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n## Design\n### Component Relationships\n| Component | Role | Dependencies |\n|-----------|------|--------------|\n| JWTService | Token 签发与验证 | KeyManager, Config |\n| AuthMiddleware | HTTP 请求认证 | JWTService |\n| KeyManager | 密钥管理 | Config |\n| TokenRefresher | Token 刷新 | JWTService |\n\n## Data Structures\n```go\n// JWTConfig JWT 配置\ntype JWTConfig struct {\n    SecretKey      string        // HS256 密钥\n    PrivateKey    string        // RS256 私钥\n    PublicKey     string        // RS256 公钥\n    Algorithm     string        // HS256 或 RS256\n    TokenExpiry   time.Duration // Token 有效期\n    RefreshExpiry time.Duration // 刷新 Token 有效期\n    Issuer        string        // 签发者\n}\n\n// Claims JWT 声明\ntype Claims struct {\n    UserID   string                 `json:\"user_id\"`\n    Roles    []string               `json:\"roles\"`\n    Metadata map[string]interface{} `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    jwt.RegisteredClaims\n}\n\n// TokenPair Token 对\ntype TokenPair struct {\n    AccessToken  string `json:\"access_token\"`\n    RefreshToken string `json:\"refresh_token\"`\n    ExpiresIn    int64  `json:\"expires_in\"`\n    TokenType    string `json:\"token_type\"`\n}\n```\n\n## API Contracts\n### 签发 Token\n| Method | Path | Description |\n|--------|------|-------------|\n| POST | /auth/token | 签发新 Token |\n| POST | /auth/refresh | 刷新 Token |\n\n### Request/Response\n```go\n// TokenRequest 签发请求\ntype TokenRequest struct {\n    UserID   string                 `json:\"user_id\"`\n    Roles    []string               `json:\"roles,omitempty\"`\n    Metadata map[string]interface{} `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n}\n\n// TokenResponse 签发响应\ntype TokenResponse struct {\n    AccessToken  string `json:\"access_token\"`\n    RefreshToken string `json:\"refresh_token\"`\n    ExpiresIn    int64  `json:\"expires_in\"`\n    TokenType    string `json:\"token_type\"`\n}\n```\n\n## Error Handling\n| Error | Code | Description |\n|-------|------|-------------|\n| ErrTokenExpired | 401 | Token 已过期 |\n| ErrTokenInvalid | 401 | Token 无效 |\n| ErrTokenMissing | 401 | Token 缺失 |\n| ErrTokenRefreshFailed | 401 | Token 刷新失败 |\n\n## Testing Strategy\n- 单元测试覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n- 集成测试覆盖主要流程\n- 边界测试：过期、篡改、格式错误\n- 性能测试：Token 签发 QPS\n\n## Validation Checklist\n- [ ] JWTService 实现 Sign/Verify/Refresh 方法\n- [ ] AuthMiddleware 实现请求拦截\n- [ ] 支持 HS256 和 RS256 算法\n- [ ] 配置化过期时间\n- [ ] 完整错误处理\n\n## Open Questions\n1. 是否需要支持 Token 黑名单？\n2. 是否需要支持多租户场景？\n3. 密钥轮换策略？\n\n## References\n- [golang-jwt/jwt](https://github.com/golang-jwt/jwt)\n- [RFC 7519](https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7519)"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/design.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/design.md","time":{"start":1775852134559,"end":1775852134577}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852134580,"sessionID":"ses_286fa7576ffeYv4Qt7A9uX3m2B","part":{"id":"prt_d7908d382001JBGh2kVbqj0ENe","messageID":"msg_d79077d99001gzS5l7ZDdjIyGh","sessionID":"ses_286fa7576ffeYv4Qt7A9uX3m2B","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-ad32068bfd6a4d1ab72187f968a59177","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/tasks.md","content":"# AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 |\n| Module | `pkg/router` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Design | ST-1 |\n\n## Task Checklist\n### Phase 1: 核心数据结构 (ST-1)\n- [ ] **T1.1**: 定义 JWT 配置结构\n  - 创建 JWTConfig 结构体\n  - 支持从配置文件/环境变量读取\n  - File: `pkg/router/jwt.go`\n  - Verification: `go build ./pkg/router`\n\n- [ ] **T1.2**: 定义 Claims 结构体\n  - 扩展 jwt.RegisteredClaims\n  - 添加自定义字段\n  - File: `pkg/router/jwt.go`\n  - Verification: `go build ./pkg/router`\n\n### Phase 2: JWT 服务实现 (ST-2)\n- [ ] **T2.1**: 实现 JWTService\n  - Sign 方法：签发 Token\n  - Verify 方法：验证 Token\n  - Refresh 方法：刷新 Token\n  - File: `pkg/router/jwt.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router -run TestJWTService -v`\n\n- [ ] **T2.2**: 实现 KeyManager\n  - 支持 HS256 密钥管理\n  - 支持 RS256 密钥对管理\n  - 密钥加载与验证\n  - File: `pkg/router/jwt.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router -run TestKeyManager -v`\n\n### Phase 3: 认证中间件 (ST-3)\n- [ ] **T3.1**: 实现 AuthMiddleware\n  - Token 解析\n  - Token 验证\n  - Claims 注入上下文\n  - File: `pkg/router/middleware/auth.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router/middleware -run TestAuthMiddleware -v`\n\n- [ ] **T3.2**: 实现错误处理\n  - 统一错误响应格式\n  - 日志记录\n  - File: `pkg/router/middleware/auth.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router/middleware -run TestAuthErrors -v`\n\n### Phase 4: 测试与文档 (ST-4)\n- [ ] **T4.1**: 单元测试\n  - JWTService 测试\n  - KeyManager 测试\n  - AuthMiddleware 测试\n  - File: `pkg/router/jwt_test.go`, `pkg/router/middleware/auth_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router/... -cover`\n\n- [ ] **T4.2**: 集成测试\n  - 完整认证流程测试\n  - 刷新流程测试\n  - File: `pkg/router/jwt_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test ./pkg/router -run TestIntegration -v`\n\n## Task Dependencies\n```\nT1.1 ──┬── T2.1 ──┬── T3.1 ── T4.1\n       │          │\nT1.2 ──┴── T2.2 ──┴── T3.2 ── T4.2\n```\n\n## Verification Commands\n| Task | Verification Command |\n|------|----------------------|\n| T1.1, T1.2 | `go build ./pkg/router` |\n| T2.1 | `go test ./pkg/router -run TestJWTService -v` |\n| T2.2 | `go test ./pkg/router -run TestKeyManager -v` |\n| T3.1 | `go test ./pkg/router/middleware -run TestAuthMiddleware -v` |\n| T3.2 | `go test ./pkg/router/middleware -run TestAuthErrors -v` |\n| T4.1 | `go test ./pkg/router/... -cover` |\n| T4.2 | `go test ./pkg/router -run TestIntegration -v` |\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] JWT Token 签发功能正常\n- [ ] Token 验证中间件正确拦截无效请求\n- [ ] Token 刷新机制工作正常\n- [ ] 支持 HS256 和 RS256 算法\n- [ ] 测试覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n- [ ] 所有验证命令通过\n\n## Files Modified/Created\n| File | Status | Description |\n|------|--------|-------------|\n| `pkg/router/jwt.go` | Created | JWT 核心功能实现 |\n| `pkg/router/jwt_test.go` | Created | JWT 单元测试 |\n| `pkg/router/middleware/auth.go` | Created | 认证中间件 |\n| `pkg/router/middleware/auth_test.go` | Created | 中间件测试 |\n\n## Notes\n- 使用 golang-jwt/jwt v5 作为基础库\n- 遵循 Go 标准项目布局\n- 注意线程安全性\n\n## Implementation Timeline\n| Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n|-------|-------|--------|------------|\n| Phase 1 | T1.1, T1.2 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 2 | T2.1, T2.2 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 3 | T3.1, T3.2 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 4 | T4.1, T4.2 | Not Started | 0% |"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775852134562,"end":1775852134579}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852134582,"sessionID":"ses_286fa7576ffeYv4Qt7A9uX3m2B","part":{"id":"prt_d79092079001AT3ZtfeXTugfHV","messageID":"msg_d79077d99001gzS5l7ZDdjIyGh","sessionID":"ses_286fa7576ffeYv4Qt7A9uX3m2B","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-b7c477fb65354ec0adef69895edcb235","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/delta-spec.md","content":"# Delta Spec: AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发\n\n**Module:** `pkg/router`\n**Language:** Go\n**Size:** M\n\n## Overview\n为 Router 模块添加 JWT 认证与签发能力，包括 Token 签发、验证和刷新功能。\n\n## GIVEN/WHEN/THEN Scenarios\n### Requirement: JWT Token 签发\n#### Scenario: 使用 HS256 算法签发 Token\n- **GIVEN** 配置了有效的 HS256 密钥\n- **WHEN** 调用 Sign 方法签发 Token\n- **THEN** 返回有效的 JWT Token\n\n#### Scenario: 使用 RS256 算法签发 Token\n- **GIVEN** 配置了有效的 RSA 密钥对\n- **WHEN** 调用 Sign 方法签发 Token\n- **THEN** 返回有效的 JWT Token\n\n### Requirement: JWT Token 验证\n#### Scenario: 验证有效 Token\n- **GIVEN** 有效的 JWT Token\n- **WHEN** 调用 Verify 方法验证 Token\n- **THEN** 返回解析后的 Claims\n\n#### Scenario: 拒绝过期 Token\n- **GIVEN** 已过期的 JWT Token\n- **WHEN** 调用 Verify 方法验证 Token\n- **THEN** 返回 ErrTokenExpired 错误\n\n#### Scenario: 拒绝篡改 Token\n- **GIVEN** 被篡改的 JWT Token\n- **WHEN** 调用 Verify 方法验证 Token\n- **THEN** 返回 ErrTokenInvalid 错误\n\n### Requirement: Token 刷新\n#### Scenario: 刷新有效 Token\n- **GIVEN** 有效的 Refresh Token\n- **WHEN** 调用 Refresh 方法\n- **THEN** 返回新的 TokenPair\n\n#### Scenario: 拒绝无效刷新\n- **GIVEN** 无效或过期的 Refresh Token\n- **WHEN** 调用 Refresh 方法\n- **THEN** 返回 ErrTokenRefreshFailed 错误\n\n### Requirement: 认证中间件\n#### Scenario: 通过有效 Token 的请求\n- **GIVEN** HTTP 请求包含有效 Authorization Header\n- **WHEN** 请求经过 AuthMiddleware\n- **THEN** 请求被放行，Claims 注入上下文\n\n#### Scenario: 拒绝无 Token 的请求\n- **GIVEN** HTTP 请求不包含 Authorization Header\n- **WHEN** 请求经过 AuthMiddleware\n- **THEN** 返回 401 Unauthorized 响应\n\n#### Scenario: 拒绝无效 Token 的请求\n- **GIVEN** HTTP 请求包含无效 Token\n- **WHEN** 请求经过 AuthMiddleware\n- **THEN** 返回 401 Unauthorized 响应\n\n## Implementation Files\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `pkg/router/jwt.go` | JWT 核心功能（Sign/Verify/Refresh） |\n| `pkg/router/jwt_test.go` | JWT 单元测试 |\n| `pkg/router/middleware/auth.go` | HTTP 认证中间件 |\n| `pkg/router/middleware/auth_test.go` | 中间件测试 |\n\n## Dependencies\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5 | JWT 标准库 |\n| pkg/config | 配置管理 |\n| pkg/logger | 日志记录 |\n\n## Validation Checklist\n- [ ] JWT Token 签发功能正常\n- [ ] Token 验证中间件正确拦截无效请求\n- [ ] Token 刷新机制工作正常\n- [ ] 支持 HS256 和 RS256 算法\n- [ ] 测试覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n- [ ] 无安全漏洞（密钥不硬编码）"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/delta-spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775852134565,"end":1775852134580}}}}
